Description: Powerful Phishing Tool with 50+ templates
 Dark-Phish is a comprehensive phishing framework offering over 50
 ready‑to‑use templates (e.g., Facebook, Instagram, Netflix). It
 includes an interactive setup menu, automated ngrok tunnel creation,
 and real‑time credential logging via local web server.
